OL,3,CWhat's a homeless health nurse and
OL,4,Cwhat work do they do?
OL,6,FWhen I got a press release from the
OL,7,FSouth Eastern Health Trust about the
OL,8,Fwork of their homeless health nurse,
OL,9,Fit piqued my interest.
OL,11,FI had never heard of such a service so
OL,12,FI was eager to ask Lisa Ewart what
OL,13,Fexactly her role entails.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
