CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772719870
OL,3,CWhat's a homeless health nurse and
OL,4,Cwhat work do they do?
OL,6,FShe said: "I work with all of the
OL,7,Fhostels and the refuges within the
OL,8,FSouth Eastern Trust area and I also
OL,9,Ftry to advocate for and support the
OL,10,Fpeople who are on the streets. We
OL,11,Fwould look at the barriers of trying
OL,12,Fto access health services so getting
OL,13,Fthem access to GPs and into primary
OL,14,Fcare would be the first thing."
OL,16,FUnlike a traditional nurse or clinic,
OL,17,FLisa goes to her patients where they
OL,18,Fare to meet their needs and lifestyles.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
