PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772719870
OL,3,CWhat's a homeless health nurse and
OL,4,Cwhat work do they do?
OL,6,FIt sounds basic but that different
OL,7,Fapproach of bringing the services to
OL,8,Fthe service users can make a massive
OL,9,Fdifference to those who need that.
OL,11,F"You just look at the basics," Lisa
OL,12,Fsays. "Build a little trust with the
OL,13,Fservice users. Just having a chat with
OL,14,Fthem. Maybe not going in with the
OL,15,Fclipboard and questions. Just trying
OL,16,Fto build up a relationship with them
OL,17,Fand I think we are in an advantageous
OL,18,Fposition in the services we offer.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772719870
OL,3,CWhat's a homeless health nurse and
OL,4,Cwhat work do they do?
OL,6,F"So just meeting the service users
OL,7,Fwhere they are at and bringing the
OL,8,Fcare to them so they don't have any
OL,9,Fmore barriers to face ... if you bring
OL,10,Fit to them, they will engage with the
OL,11,Fservice."
OL,13,FLisa says since beginning her role,
OL,14,Fher perception of those who are
OL,15,Fclassed as homeless has been
OL,16,Fchallenged.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
