CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772719870
OL,3,CWhat's a homeless health nurse and
OL,4,Cwhat work do they do?
OL,6,FShe says: "For women we see, it's
OL,7,Fmassive and it's so much more hidden
OL,8,Ffor females. I work with families who
OL,9,Fare homeless and who are in hostels
OL,10,Fand not everybody sees that.
OL,12,F"It's not the stereotypical sleeping
OL,13,Fbags in doorways or begging. That's
OL,14,Fnot homelessness. We are only
OL,15,Fscratching the surface. Hidden
OL,16,Fhomelessness is massive. We're only a
OL,17,Fcouple of pay checks away from poverty
OL,18,Fand homelessness ourselves."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
