OL,3,CWhat's a homeless health nurse and
OL,4,Cwhat work do they do?
OL,6,FLisa has been a nurse for many years
OL,7,Fand admits that this role of homeless
OL,8,Fhealth nurse comes with its challenges
OL,9,Fbut it's clear when she speaks just
OL,10,Fhow much she loves her job.
OL,12,F"It's not for the faint-hearted," Lisa
OL,13,Fsays. "I think you need to have a bit
OL,14,Fof life experience.
OL,16,F"But the service users are great. It's
OL,17,Fso rewarding. You feel like you're
OL,18,Fmaking a difference and the service
OL,19,Fusers are really thankful even just
OL,20,Ffor the smallest things that you do
OL,21,Ffor them so it's brilliant."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
